Class Colord

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Double>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Double>, java.util.List<java.lang.Double>

    public class Colord
extends Vector3d
    An RGB color specified using floating point accuracy. This is most useful for operations common in ray-tracing applications, as well as HDR and similar features.
    Author:
    eschweic
